OL,3,CFour-day week pilot hailed a success
OL,5,FThe latest national four-day working
OL,6,Fweek pilot, involving 17 companies and
OL,7,Fnearly 1,000 workers, has ended with a
OL,8,F100% success rate, it was announced on
OL,9,FThursday.
OL,11,FAll 17 companies have decided to
OL,12,Fcontinue working a shorter working
OL,13,Fweek at the end of the trial.
OL,15,FThe six-month trial began last
OL,16,FNovember and was organised by the 4
OL,17,FDay Week Foundation.
