OL,3,CFour-day week pilot hailed a success
OL,5,FOrganisations were able to maintain
OL,6,Fservice levels and key performance
OL,7,Findicators whilst observing several
OL,8,Fbenefits for employee wellbeing, said
OL,9,Fthe report.
OL,11,FAlmost two-thirds of workers
OL,12,Fregistered a reduction in how often
OL,13,Fthey experienced burnout, two in five
OL,14,Ffound an improvement in their mental
OL,15,Fhealth and almost half said they felt
OL,16,Fmore satisfied with life.
