OL,3,CFour-day week pilot hailed a success
OL,5,FJoe Ryle, campaign director of the 4
OL,6,FDay Week Foundation, said: "With
OL,7,Fgreater knowledge, expertise and
OL,8,Fexperience of what it takes to
OL,9,Fsuccessfully implement a four-day
OL,10,Fweek, we're really pleased to see such
OL,11,Fa high success rate.
OL,13,F"People are happier, businesses are
OL,14,Fthriving, and there's no turning back.
OL,16,F"We've proved it again and again: a
OL,17,Ffour-day week works and should now be
OL,18,Fimplemented more widely across the
OL,19,Feconomy."
