OL,3,CFour-day week pilot hailed a success
OL,5,FAlan Brunt, chief executive of Bron
OL,6,FAfon Community Housing with 420 staff,
OL,7,Fwho are extending their pilot further,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Almost as soon as we started
OL,9,Ftalking about it, our teams got
OL,10,Ftogether to set about making it work
OL,11,Fwhich was brilliant.
OL,13,F"We've closely monitored our
OL,14,Fperformance and customer satisfaction.
OL,15,FWe're happy with the results so far
OL,16,Fand will continue to make sure we're
OL,17,Fdelivering for our customers.
OL,19,F"I expect that most organisations will
OL,20,Fbe doing this in the next 10 years or
OL,21,Fso."
